channel.title: Zipexception: Error reading zip file! [WILL + REP] [cache error]
channel.description:
I delete my cache file, then i run the client, it downloads perfectly then the client will say "Error loading...Please report!"
The cmd gives me this error. [code] java.util.zip.zipexception: error reading zip file at java.util.zip.zipfile.read(native method) at java.util.zip.zipfile.access$1400(unknown source) at java.util.zip.zipfile.$zipfileinputstream.read(unknown source) at java.util.zip.zipfile.$zipfileinflaterinputstream.fill(unknown source)
at java.util.zip.inflaterinputstream.read(unknown source) at java.io.filterinputstream.read(unknown source) at update.writestream(update.java:43) at update.unzipfile(update.java:66:) at update.(init)(update.java:29) at client.streamloaderforname(client.java:4766) at client.startup(client.java:9057) at RSApplet.run(rsapplet.java:33) at client.(client.java:6073) at java.lang.thread.run(unknown source)[/code]
If you have any information on how to fix this please post below. Thank you.
